Amit Yadav was driving his red Honda Civic up to 25 miles over speed limit . 
 Yadav lost control of his car and smashed into an oncoming Renault Cleo . 
 Two passengers - brothers Haider, 20, and Taimur Kayani, 17 - were killed . 
 Yadav was found guilty of causing death by dangerous driving in February . 
 